American Dream Builders - Season 1, Episode 2




Mid-Century Makeover

The 11 remaining contestants report for their next challenge: a pair of neglected mid-century homes in Palm Springs, CA. The owners are looking to retain their homes' classic styles but to update them -- and transform their outdoor spaces into something special.




Original Air Date: 30-Mar-2014
